node.text: First of all, pls excuse my band-aid 😂As some of you may know after my breast augmentation I lost lots of muscle mass and motivation for the gym. Once I was recovered from the surgery, I personally got super bored of the same old workouts and music. Thankfully Eric at Dogpound LA has helped me change my routine and spice up my workouts! Hopefully this helps you gain some motivation for the gym! LONG STORY SHORT: SPICE UP YO LIFE
